high_descs: Walk around to the left and turn right to face the plate on the left end of the table.
Pick up the plate on the table.
Turn around and walk forward to the living room table, then turn right and walk forward to face the lamp in the corner of the room.
Turn on the lamp to examine the plate.
anns.task_desc: To examine a plate by lamp light.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the end of the table, turn right to get to the front of the table, then turn to your right once more so that you are facing the long end of the table.
Pick up the plate in front of the chair to your left.
Turn around and go into the living room, make a right at the coffee table, and go to the floor lamp in the far right corner of the living room.
Turn on the lamp in the corner of the living room.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the living room light.

high_descs: Turn to the left, and right to face the table on the right side.
Pick up the plate from the table, close the to the left edge.
Carry the plate and turn around. Turn right at the coffee table and then right again to find the lamp.
Hold the plate and turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Hold a plate and turn on the lamp.
